---
title: Smokey Beef & Charred Pineapple Burger with Cheesy Potato Fries, Burger Sauce & Fried Egg
description: We know some people have mixed feelings about pineapple on pizza, but how about on a burger? We argue that it gives this beef burger that extra fresh edge. If that hasn’t piqued your interest, what about adding an egg, because everyone loves an egg! Trust us, this is the new and improved burger.
